{"tid":1951399,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾醒明訴說無綫公關敗仗","createTime":"2020-03-31T03:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T03:15:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e82c98d4cddb3f36f0da1ec947adb0e94971422","tid":1951399,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200331/FMQQSEIC3HNA4OHB6U44EBS5EA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200331%2FFMQQSEIC3HNA4OHB6U44EBS5EA%2F&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtKof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=b73a0726\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200331%2FFMQQSEIC3HNA4OHB6U44EBS5EA%2F&h=f6147111\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200331/FMQQSEIC3HNA4OHB6U44EBS5EA/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾醒明訴說無綫公關敗仗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200331/large/1585577825_053d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200331%2Flarge%2F1585577825_053d.jpg&h=7439f906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾醒明（中）昨日到葉家寶（左）和黃守東的網台接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n資深公關曾醒明效力無綫多年，離職後曾加入亞視及現職的開電視擔任公關宣傳工作。昨日他獲邀到觀塘接受葉家寶和黃守東的節目訪問，三代不同公關細訴過往戰績。<br />\n<br />\n葉家寶與曾醒明相識40多年，兩人曾經分別是亞視和無綫公關，商場如戰場，曾醒明說：「交惡就冇，最深刻係2001年度香港小姐時，亞視舉辦百萬富翁少林足球名人版，當時為爭取宣傳曝光，同巴士媒體合作，播放港姐招募同宣傳片，反應好好，但公司突然煞停，怪責我幫人哋宣傳，後來亞視知道後立刻乘虛而入，攝咗個宣傳位，更難忘係當晚港姐決賽係楊思琦冠軍，收視罕有地輸咗成條街，相差六十幾萬觀眾，從來未試過。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：卓寶花 攝影：林賓尼"}]}